on identifying and deploying the best possible solution." btm_space="5%"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544590562302{margin-right: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 10% !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530613351227{padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4"][hanor_services service_style="service-four" open_link="" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="pe-7s-science" service_title="url:%230|title:Web%20Analytics||" background_overlay_color="rgba(0,0,0,0.7)" title_color="#ffffff" title_hover_color="#f7f7f7" content_color="#ffffff"]We’ll truly question your challenge, create fresh hypotheses around where the site seo results may positive.[/hanor_services][/vc_column][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530613356598{padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4"][hanor_services service_style="service-four" open_link="" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="pe-7s-anchor" service_title="url:%230|title:Business%20Goal||" background_overlay_color="rgba(0,0,0,0.7)" title_color="#ffffff" title_hover_color="#f4f4f4" content_color="#ffffff"]We get under the skin of the issue by exploring your targets and sales from intriguing new views.[/hanor_services][/vc_column][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530613362573{padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4"][hanor_services service_style="service-four" open_link="" image_icon="icon-tab" service_icon="pe-7s-sun" service_title="url:%230|title:Email%20Management||" background_overlay_color="rgba(0,0,0,0.7)" title_color="#ffffff" title_hover_color="#f7f7f7" content_color="#ffffff"]We support all new businesses through the pilot stage, creatively problem-solving the tests in business.[/hanor_services][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544590584454{padding-top: 7% !important;padding-bottom: 10% !important;background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}"][vc_column][havnor_promo promo_style="promo-two" toggle_align="true" promo_icon_image="icon-telescope" promo_title="Enterprise Mobility" promo_button_text="START FREE TRAIL" promo_button_link="#0" video_link="" open_link="true"]We create and deliver solutions that manage risk, optimize benefits, cultivate talent, and expand the power of money to protect and encourage institutions and people.[/havnor_promo][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1536319171134{padding-top: 5% !important;}"][vc_column][havnor_section_title title_align="center" title_text="Frequently Asked Questions" content_text="Services focus on our clients' most critical issues and opportunities." btm_space="5%" title_size="36px" title_btm="0px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1536319502932{padding-bottom: 8% !important;}"][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_accordion accordion_style="style-one"][vc_accordion_tab title="What does SEO stand for?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]SEO stands for Search Engine Optimization. You engage in SEO when you attempt to get a page to rank higher in a search engine’s SERPs (search engine results pages), with the ultimate goal being to increase organic (unpaid) traffic to that page.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Which is better, SEO or PPC?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]SEO and PPC (pay-per-click). You couldn’t establish domain authority, organic brand affinity, and really, a wholly formed online presence without SEO. By the same token, you couldn’t granularly target prospects by demographic, behaviors, or keywords without PPC.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where can I study SEO?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]There are a ton of great resources out there if you’re trying to learn SEO. If you’re short on cash, check out blogs like Search Engine Journal, Moz, Search Engine Land, Marketing Land, SEMPost, and the blog of all blogs, WordStream’s. We also put together a great guide on SEO basics. If not, splurge on a book like The Art of Seo, or on classes by Udemy or Lynda.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Which SEO software is best?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Again, you could come up with a good argument for a few different answers here. Ahrefs is great for competitor content and backlink research; Moz Pro’s content explorer is great for finding unlinked mentions; and SEMrush is great for rank and visibility tracking. The three share many overlapping features. It’s more a matter of preference than anything. Spyfu, AWR Cloud, and DeepCrawl are also worth checking out.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="How do backlinks affect my rankings?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Backlinks help improve your rankings. Search engines see backlinks as positive ‘votes’ for your site. Search engines highly associate your site’s backlinks with your site’s ability to satiate a browser’s search wishes..[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Best way to determine online budget?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Determine your potential return on investment. Online marketing tactics help bring more traffic and business to your site, raising your revenue. There is always a need for online marketing; however, be sure your provider is presenting you with quantifiable results.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What About Refunds?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]We are very focused on our customer amusement by delivering top quality products and support. If you are encountering any technical issues – please open a comfort ticket or visit our help center and our team will assist you in resolving your issues.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_accordion accordion_style="style-one"][vc_accordion_tab title="What are meta descriptions and do they still matter?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]A meta description is the text that appears below your page in a search engine result that explains what the page is all about. In this example, the meta description is "Learn the elements needed to write a comprehensive blog post in just 9 easy steps."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="How is SEO changing?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]SEO is always changing. But the biggest change continues to be the shift toward mobile. Mobile digital media time in the US is now significantly higher (51%) than desktop digital media time (42%), and that number is set to continue to grow. Google recently made mobile page speed a ranking factor. Going forward, if you haven’t already done so, you should look into Accelerated Mobile Pages. It’s becoming more and more paramount to make sure you have no mobile usability issues on your site.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where do I start my SEO strategy?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]What have you done thus far? If the answer is nothing, you’re going to want to use one of the SEO tools I mentioned above to run a site audit. This will allow you to find and rectify any broken links, make sure all your meta tags are in order, and check page load speeds. Search Console also has a great “Crawl Errors” tool, in addition to other tools that help you diagnose your site’s speed and usability. Once your current pages are in order, get cracking on keyword research, and start putting out some content![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What is keyword research?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Great question! Keyword research helps you determine the keywords for which you should optimize the current and future pages of your site. For example: if your new small business sells employee scheduling software, but you discover that “employee scheduling tool” has higher search volume and lower competition than “employee scheduling software,” you might want to change the copy on your website to reflect that. [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What are Page Titles &amp; Meta Description tags?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Page Titles are one of the best ways to define what a particular URL contains for the search engines and needs to be optimized properly for a URL to rank for a specific term.

The Meta Description also helps browsers understand what your site’s pages are about. This is also an opportunity to put some text in front of the potential visitor on the SERP to entice them to click. While optimization is important here, useful information and calls to action also need to be considered depending on the URL.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What is Google Webmaster Tools?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]Determine your potential return on investment. Online marketing tactics help bring more traffic and business to your site, raising your revenue. There is always a need for online marketing; however, be sure your provider is presenting you with quantifiable results.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="How long does it normally take to see SEO Results?" sub_title="Sub Title 1"][vc_column_text]When a browser conducts a search, they will be confronted by both organic results and paid results (those which are highlighted and usually placed on the very top or right-hand side of the page). While Paid Advertising is a great way to get you in front of people quickly, it is the quest of every business to achieve first-page, organic-SEO results because you no longer need to pay every time someone clicks on your site.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" overlay_dotted="" css=".vc_custom_1544599445819{padding-top: 5% !important;padding-bottom: 5% !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1530355643049{padding-top: 0px !important;}"][hanor_client_carousel open_link="" retina_img="true" client_style="client-two" client_logos="%5B%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%2C%7B%7D%5D" carousel_autoplay="true" carousel_mousedrag="true" carousel_nav="true"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
CONTENT;
